Spectrum

Class SpectrumLib

  • java.lang.Object
    • Spectrum.SpectrumLib
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable

    public class SpectrumLib
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable, java.io.Serializable
    This class represent a spectral library, it contains two views on the spectral library, a Map view that index the spectra by its peptide and a List view that contains all the spectra
    Author:
    Jian
